    <note>He(4) Yunzhong [688] He moved to Taizhou from Caizhou in ca. 1131. Father-in-law of Zhu(1) Shengfei's [8039] son, Di(sic Shang?)qing [529]. Still listed as a Meizhou jinshi in Sichuan TZ, 122.45a, an anachronistic listing of a famous former resident since it is unlikely that Yunzhong's three patrilineal ancestors would all hold office without at least one earning the jinshi. His wife, born Deng, died in 1141. Chicheng zhi, 34.22a; Han Yuanji, WJ, 20.24a-32a; XNYL, 134.3b. CBD, 4, 2933-5.</note>
